<h1>Add/Edit Appointments</h1>
<p class="whs1">The Appointments screen allows to stay on top of important events. You can schedule appointments and specify whether it should occur repeatedly. SelectionSheet.Com will block out the time in your schedule, helping you to avoid scheduling conflicts with others appointments. You can also specify whether a reminder email is sent to you when it is time to go to an appointment.</p>
<p class="whs1">To add and manage appointments, do the following:</p>
<ol>
<li class="kadov-p-ClistNumbered">
<p class="listNumbered">Select <span style="font-weight:bold;"><b>Schedules &gt; Appointments</b></span>. <a class="dropspot" href="javascript:kadovTextPopup(this)" id="a1">The Appointments screen displays.</a></p>
<div class="droptext" id="POPUP94310478" style="display:'none'; x-ss-type:dropdown;">
<p><img src="appointment1.jpg" width="804px" height="516px" border="0" class="img_whs2" alt=""></p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="kadov-p-ClistNumbered">
<p class="listNumbered">Click <span style="font-weight:bold;"><b>Add Event</b></span>, or click <span style="font-weight:bold;"><b>add</b></span> on a day in the calender or select an appointment to edit. <a class="dropspot" href="javascript:kadovTextPopup(this)" id="a2">The Appointments Add Event screen displays.</a></p>
<div class="droptext" id="POPUP211169190" style="display:'none'; x-ss-type:dropdown;">
<p><img src="appointmentsnew.jpg" width="555px" height="536px" border="0" class="img_whs3" alt=""></p>
</div>
</li>
<li class="kadov-p-ClistNumbered">
<p class="listNumbered">Enter or change information in the appropriate fields.</p>
</li>
<li class="kadov-p-ClistNumbered">
<p class="listNumbered">Click <span style="font-weight:bold;"><b>Save</b></span>. The appointment is added to the appointment calender.</p>
</li>
</ol>
